## Frontend architecture

### Provider tree (`main.jsx`)
```
StrictMode
  DirectionProvider (initialDirection from html lang)
    MantineProvider (defaultColorScheme="dark")
      MantineDirectionSync
      Notifications (position="top-right")
      BrowserRouter
        AuthProvider
          AppRoutes (App.jsx)
```

### Routing (`App.jsx`) ‚Äî React Router v7, NOT file-based
| Path | Access | Page | Notes |
|------|--------|------|-------|
| `/login` | Public | `LoginPage` | Redirects to `/` if logged in; `?reason=expired` banner |
| `/register` | Public | `RegisterPage` | Redirects to `/` if logged in |
| `/` | Protected | `HomePage` | Leaderboard embedded here ‚Äî no `/leaderboard` route |
| `/games` | Protected | `AllGamesPage` | Full tournament schedule |
| `/profile` | Protected | `ProfilePage` | Account + tournament bets + prediction history |
| `/rules` | Protected | `RulesPage` | Static i18n rules content |
| `/scorers` | Protected | `TopScorersPage` | Aggregated tournament-bet picks |
| `/admin` | Protected | `AdminPage` | User management (no server-side route guard ‚Äî UI only) |
| `*` | ‚Äî | Redirect to `/` | Catch-all |

**Guards:**
- `ProtectedRoute` waits for `authReady` (boot `/auth/me` probe) before redirecting to `/login`.
- Protected routes wrap content in `AppLayout` = `SimulationBanner` + `Navbar` + `{children}`.
- Auth pages render **standalone** (no Navbar) with `LanguageSwitcher` in corner.

### Auth flow (frontend)
1. Boot: `AuthContext` calls `GET /api/auth/me` (always 200: `{ user }` or `{ user: null }`).
2. Valid session ‚Üí hydrate `user` state + `localStorage wc_user` cache.
3. `serverApi` sends `withCredentials: true`; JWT never touches JS.
4. 401 on any API call (except `/auth/me`) ‚Üí clear cache ‚Üí redirect `/login?reason=expired`.
5. PWA: `AuthContext` refetches predictions on `visibilitychange` return.

### Data hooks ‚Äî when to use which
| Hook | Used by | Purpose |
|------|---------|---------|
| `useAuth()` | All pages, Navbar, modals | user, predictions, scores, users, admin helpers |
| `useMatches()` | AllGamesPage, ProfilePage, AdminOverrideModal | Session-cached full 104-match schedule |
| `useTodayMatches({ onMatchFinished })` | HomePage | Adaptive polling; callback triggers leaderboard refresh |
| `useUserPredictions()` | HomePage, AllGamesPage | Thin wrapper over auth predictions map |
| `useMinuteTick()` | HomePage, AllGamesPage | Shared `now` Date for countdown consistency |
| `useSpotlight()` | HomePage | Daily exact-score + chaos-pick highlights |

