### Leaderboard rules (UI + backend)
- **Admins do NOT appear in the leaderboard.** Backend filters `role = 'USER'` and `status = 'APPROVED'` in `scores.routes.js`. Frontend `HomePage` also filters `u.role !== 'ADMIN'`.
- Leaderboard is on `/` only ‚Äî inline `LeaderboardTable` + `Podium`, not a separate page.
- Rank-change indicators and "you" row styling live in `HomePage.module.css`.

